description: Sergio & Catherine (hailing from Holland and Spain) fused their mutual passion for food to start The Orange Cow, which is now cruising through Atlanta and dishing out a delicious blend of Dutch and Mediterranean flavors.Their menu features a savory selection that includes…The Orange Cow Burger- meat spiced with onion and garlic, with bacon, mozzarella, onion, tomato, lettuce, smashed chips, and their very own special pineapple sauceSpecial Patat- Dutch-style fresh hot fries with mayonnaise, curry, and onionGreek Salad- with tomato, cucumber, onion, feta cheese, and olives. And there’s more, so be sure to come eat at De Orange Cow for some utterly “Wow!”- worthy food!
name: De Orange Cow
